        <span class="h">Huxley</span>
      </div>
      <div class="snav-sub">Anatomie des dystopies modernes</div>
    </div>

    <span class="snav-section-lbl">Introduction</span>
    <a href="#hero" class="snav-link act"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Présentation générale</a>
    <a href="#deux-visions" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Deux visions fondatrices</a>

    <div class="snav-divider"></div>
    <span class="snav-section-lbl">Analyse comparative</span>
    <a href="#tableau" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Tableau comparatif</a>
    <a href="#glossaire" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Lexique dystopique</a>
    <a href="#mecanismes" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Mécanismes de domination</a>

    <div class="snav-divider"></div>
    <span class="snav-section-lbl">Réseau d'auteurs</span>
    <a href="#auteurs" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>La galaxie critique</a>
    <a href="#han" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Byung-Chul Han</a>
    <a href="#debord-laboetie" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Debord & La Boétie</a>
    <a href="#bauman" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Bauman & l'amour liquide</a>

    <div class="snav-divider"></div>
    <span class="snav-section-lbl">Contemporain</span>
    <a href="#aujourd-hui" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Quelle dystopie vivons-nous ?</a>
    <a href="#reflexion" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Pistes de réflexion</a>
    <a href="#synthese" class="snav-link"><span class="snav-dot"></span>Synthèse critique</a>

    <div class="snav-footer">
      Littérature & Philosophie politique<br>
      Cours comparatif · L3 / M1<br>
